-- Identifier of a package alias is identical to the identifier of an imported property set.
-- No bug SC0023.
PACKAGE TC2
    PUBLIC
        WITH propSetId, pckgId::pckgId;
        propSetId renames package pckgId::pckgId; -- no bug SC0023
END TC2;

 

PROPERTY SET propSetId is

    simpleProp : AADLINTEGER => 0 APPLIES TO (ABSTRACT);   
END propSetId;

 

PACKAGE pckgId::pckgId
    PUBLIC

      

       THREAD myThr

        END myThr;


END pckgId::pckgId;
